Dia. 01 Life?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par How about expanding Black's eye-space with 1?
\par If White plays at 2, Black can live easily with 3.
\par
\par However this variation was Black's wishful thinking. Black is \cf1\b missed \cf0\b0 a very\cf1\b  important thing\cf0\b0 .
\par In other words, White is not going to play the hane at 2.
\par
\par }
