Dia. 02 Placement
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After Black \'a1\'e3, White destroys the eye-shape from 1 to 3 and Black can't live anymore.
\par
\par Actually if Black directly plays the placement at 3 instead of 1, Black is captured again.
\par
\par Pay attention that Black lived immediately in the previous diagram when he got to play at 3.
\par
\par }
