Dia. 03 Death in Hane
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black can't live with 1 either.
\par Following the Baduk proverb which says "\cf1\b There is death in the hane\cf0\b0 ", White plays at 2 and 4 then the placement at 6.
\par
\par White can also play at 6 instead of 4.
\par However if White plays at 6 instead of 2, Black can live with A.
\par }
