Dia. 05 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Have you heard about the proverb which says, "\cf1\b the vital point is in the center of the symmetrical shape\cf0\b0 "?
\par
\par Yes, that's right. Therefore Black 1 is the vital point.
\par
\par After White 2 and Black 3, A and B are miai so Black is alive.
\par }
